## Contribution and Issues

We appreciate any assistance in making DossIO even better!

Please refer to [Google's Java Style Guide](https://google.github.io/styleguide/javaguide.html) for
guidance. Make sure to run the
<code>check.sh</code> or <code>check.bat</code> commands to keep your code consistent and check
for common java errors!

When commiting your changes, make sure to structure them like this:  
<code>[title]: Give a tag and general title describing your commit.</code>  
<code>[body1]: Give a detailed technical explanation of how your commit works.</code>  
<code>[body2]: Give a short description on why your commit is useful.</code>  
<code>[optional]: Create a bullet point list of additions and changes.</code>

Please report any major issues you come across, even if you don't have the technical knowledge
(all issues/bug reports are helpful)!
